IOSOS|website=basketdominicano.info|language=es|archive-date=February 15, 2016|date=2011|access-date=April 20, 2020}}</ref>\n|-\n|Sureste: {{flagicon|USA}} {{sortname|Eddie|Basden}}\t\n|[[Cocolos de San Pedro de Macor\u00eds]]\n|-\n|2012\t\n|{{flagicon|USA}} {{sortname|Robert|Glenn|dab=basketball}}\t\t\n|[[Indios de San Francisco de Macor\u00eds]]\n|<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://listindiario.com/el-deporte/2012/09/08/246478/glenn-es-premiado-como-mas-valioso|title=Glenn es premiado como M\u00e1s Valioso|newspaper=List\u00edn Diario|date=September 8, 2012|language=es|access-date=April 20, 2020}}</ref>\n|-\n|2013\t\n|{{flagicon|USA}} {{sortname|Gary|Flowers}}\n|[[Titanes del Licey]]\n|<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://listindiario.com/el-deporte/2013/08/12/287995/gary-flowers-es-nombrado-jugador-mas-valioso-de-lnb|title=Gary Flowers es nombrado Jugador M\u00e1s Valioso de LNB|newspaper=List\u00edn Diario|date=August 12, 2013|language=es|access-date=April 20, 2020}}</ref>\n|-\n|2014\t\n|{{flagicon|DOM}} {{sortname|Gerardo|Suero}}\n|[[Titanes del Distrito Nacional]]\n|<ref>{{Cite news|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160411110157/http://www.lnb.com.do/home/asi-va-la-liga/216-gerardo-suero-es-nombrado-jugador-mas-valioso-de-la-serie-regular-temporada-2014-de-la-lnb|url=http://www.lnb.com.do/home/asi-va-la-liga/216-gerardo-suero-es-nombrado-jugador-mas-valioso-de-la-serie-regular-temporada-2014-de-la-lnb|title=Gerardo Suero es nombrado Jugador M\u00e1s Valioso de la serie regular temporada 2014 de la LNB|website=lnb.com.do|date=June 23, 2014|archive-date=April 11, 2016|language=es|access-date=April 20, 2020}}</ref>\n|-\n|2015\t\n|{{flagicon|USA}} {{sortname|Reyshawn|Terry}}\n|[[Ca\u00f1eros del Este]]\n|<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.elcaribe.com.do/2015/07/16/reyshawn-terry-jugador-mas-valioso-liga-nacional-baloncesto|title=Reyshawn Terry Jugador M\u00e1s Valioso de la Liga Nacional de Baloncesto|author=M\u00e9ndez, Orlando|date=July 16, 2015|newspaper=El Caribe|acce