cia-el-equipo-todos-estrellas|title=La Lidoba anuncia el equipo Todos Estrellas|language=es|newspaper=[[List\u00edn Diario]]|date=October 5, 2007|access-date=April 20, 2020}}</ref>\n|-\n|2008\n|{{flagicon|DOM}} {{sortname|Richard|Ortega}}\n|[[Indios de San Francisco de Macor\u00eds]]\n|<ref>{{Cite news|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160408210805/http://www.melvynlopez.com/2008/10/lidoba-all-star-2008-melvyn-lopez-es.html|url=http://www.melvynlopez.com/2008/10/lidoba-all-star-2008-melvyn-lopez-es.html|title=LIDOBA presenta all star 2008 & Melvyn Lopez es elegido como el manager del a\u00f1o|website=melvynlopez.com|archive-date=April 8, 2016|language=es|access-date=April 20, 2020}}</ref>\n|-\n|2009\n|colspan=3|<center>''No league held''</center>\n|-\n|rowspan=2|2010\t\n|Norte: {{flagicon|USA}} {{sortname|Tyron|Thomas}}\n|[[Indios de San Francisco de Macor\u00eds]]\n|rowspan=2|<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://listindiario.com/el-deporte/2010/09/29/160679/maurice-carter-y-tyron-thomas-ganan-premios-mvp-en-la-lnb|title=Maurice Carter y Tyron Thomas ganan premios MVP en la LNB|newspaper=List\u00edn Diario|date=September 29, 2010|language=es|access-date=April 20, 2020}}</ref>\n|-\n|Sureste: {{flagicon|USA}} {{sortname|Maurice|Carter|dab=basketball, born 1983}}\n|[[Ca\u00f1eros de La Romana]]\n|-\n|rowspan=2|2011\t\n|Norte: {{flagicon|DOM}} {{sortname|Juan|Coronado}}\n|[[Reales de La Vega]]\n|rowspan=2|<ref>{{Cite news|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160215164734/http://www.basketdominicano.info/2011/09/lnb-coronado-y-basden-fueron-escogidos.html|url=http://www.basketdominicano.info/2011/09/lnb-coronado-y-basden-fueron-escogidos.html|title=LNB: CORONADO Y BASDEN FUERON ESCOGIDOS COMO JUGADORES MAS VALIOSOS|website=basketdominicano.info|language=es|archive-date=February 15, 2016|date=2011|access-date=April 20, 2020}}</ref>\n|-\n|Sureste: {{flagicon|USA}} {{sortname|Eddie|Basden}}\t\n|[[Cocolos de San Pedro de Macor\u00eds]]\n|-\n|2012\t\n|{{flagicon|USA}} {{